      <title>随着利率上涨消退，新加坡银行利润将达到顶峰</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-banks-profits-set-peak-rates-boost-fades-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率上升，新加坡银行第四季度的利润预计将更高，但随着大型央行转向降息以及波动的市场对其主要财富业务造成压力，增长势头可能会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-banks-profits-set-peak-rates-boost-fades-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，腾讯正在开发热门主机游戏《Elden Ring》的移动版本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-working-mobile-version-hit-console-game-elden-ring-sources-say-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名知情人士表示，中国腾讯控股一直在努力将广受好评的动作角色扮演游戏《Elden Ring》改编成手机版本，同时也在寻找新的热门游戏来刷新其老化的游戏库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-working-mobile-version-hit-console-game-elden-ring-sources-say-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:23:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理：央行有降息空间</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-pm-there-is-room-central-bank-cut-rates-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理Srettha Thavisin周二再次呼吁央行降息，称降息25个基点将帮助民众，而不是加剧通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-pm-there-is-room-central-bank-cut-rates-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 04:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚 Myer 股价跃升至 11 个月高点，因零售商挑战惨淡预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australias-myer-jumps-11-month-high-retailer-challenges-dismal-expectations-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，迈尔控股 (Myer Holdings) 股价飙升至 11 个月高点，此前该零售商在应对生活成本危机影响的过程中上半年销售额超出了市场预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australias-myer-jumps-11-month-high-retailer-challenges-dismal-expectations-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行维持利率不变，警告可能进一步加息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-central-bank-holds-rates-warns-further-hike-might-be-needed-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行周二如预期维持利率稳定，但警告称，鉴于通胀仍然过高，且需要看到更多证据表明物价压力正在降温，不排除进一步加息的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-central-bank-holds-rates-warns-further-hike-might-be-needed-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1990年以来澳大利亚利率变化</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australian-interest-rate-changes-since-1990-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚储备银行周二在政策会议后将现金利率维持在 4.35% 不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australian-interest-rate-changes-since-1990-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行下调通胀和增长前景，警告需求仍然过高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-cbank-trims-inflation-growth-outlook-warns-demand-still-too-high-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透悉尼4月8日 - 澳大利亚央行周二下调了通胀和经济增长预期，但暗示需求仍领先于供应，暗示不会急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-cbank-trims-inflation-growth-outlook-warns-demand-still-too-high-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:36:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示反对并打击一切形式的网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国驻菲律宾大使馆表示，中国政府不会容忍任何形式的网络攻击，也不会允许任何国家和个人利用中国基础设施从事此类非法活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管通胀放缓，菲律宾央行仍强化鹰派立场</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippine-cbank-reinforces-hawkish-stance-despite-slower-inflation-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管1月份年度通胀放缓，菲律宾央行周二仍加强了鹰派立场，因为政策制定者仍担心厄尔尼诺现象的影响可能会使第二季度消费者价格增长超过目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippine-cbank-reinforces-hawkish-stance-despite-slower-inflation-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国反弹亚洲股市上涨，美元稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于遭受重创的中国市场反弹，亚洲股市周二小幅上涨，但其他地区的投资者因美联储近期降息的预期减弱而持谨慎态度，这反过来又支撑了美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:35:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
